Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:54.95,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,PUNCAK - KETINGGIAN 1.553,3 METER
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:09.55,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 4: JANGAN BIARKAN\NORANG LAIN MENEMUKANMU
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:10.96,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,BERSAMBUNG
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Klien yang kita bahas kemarin\Ndatang bersamaku hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Aya Tsukiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wanita tak terlihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria tak terlihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini seperti Tonome yang berpakaian wanita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jaga ucapanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome berpakaian wanita...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf. Dia tidak terbiasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau Tonome?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pertama kalinya\Naku bertemu pria tak terlihat di kota.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lega karena detektif untuk kasusku\Nsatu ras denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paham perasaan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harap kami bisa membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah itu membuatmu tak nyaman?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja tidak!\NDia adalah klien!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi apakah hanya perasaanku,\Natau mereka akrab?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka jarang melihat ras mereka sendiri.\NItu normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, suara Akira memang terdengar\Nlebih lembut daripada biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, itu memang membuatmu tak nyaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lucunya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dicurigai mencuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uang di brankas perusahaan hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada seorang pun terlihat\Ndalam rekaman kamera keamanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, tiba-tiba, Wakil Presdir bertanya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa mungkin orang tak terlihat\Nyang melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kata Presdir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Presdir sedang dirawat di rumah sakit.\NWakil Presdir yang menggantikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, aku tidak melakukannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Wakil Presdir...\NTak peduli apa yang kukatakan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia menuduhku pelakunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun buktinya kurang?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlebih lagi, karena orang tak terlihat\Ntidak punya wajah untuk diidentifikasi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita perlu cara membuktikan alibinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tsukiya tidak sedang bertugas\Ndan berada di tempat lain hari itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dia bisa membuktikan\Ndia sungguh berada di tempat lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami akan lakukan yang terbaik untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih... Mohon bantuannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Wakil Presdir, Gamaike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, wanita yang dicurigai itu\Nmenyewa pengacara dan detektif?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba kulihat.\NJadi, kau juga orang tak terlihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika boleh, bisakah kau tunjukkan\Nrekaman video keamanannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku tidak keberatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak kau menutup brankas sampai\Nkau membukanya keesokan harinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak ada tanda-tanda\Norang menyentuh brankas itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ya! Seperti yang kukatakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu, orang tak terlihat\Nbisa menjadi tak terlihat sama sekali
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bahkan pakaiannya pun tak terlihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin dia menggunakan itu\Nuntuk melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana detektifnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:04:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini adalah kemampuan\Nuntuk menjadi tak terlihat sama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemampuan ini hanya membuat seseorang\Nmenjadi tak terlihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak memungkinkan kami menembus benda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, seperti yang terlihat dalam video,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak mungkin mencuri uang\Ndari brankas yang tidak pernah dibuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Ah, kalau begitu...\Naku pasti terlalu cepat menyimpulkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, tapi uang di brankas hilang,\Ndan aku kehilangan akal sehatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, kami memperoleh\Nrekaman terpisah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama beberapa hari\Nsetelah menjadi perwakilan presdir,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau pergi ke bank untuk menyetor\Nsetumpuk uang kertas tiap hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau takut akan tertangkap,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi kau berusaha memanfaatkan\Nkarakteristik Tsukiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau berpura-pura\Nuntuk membuat orang lain mencurigainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah aku salah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku, ini adalah fitnah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, dan menurutku, penggelapan juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau menjelaskannya, Nak?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}P-Presdir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kau lakukan selama aku tak ada\Nkarena radang usus buntu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em... Aku punya dorongan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu lebih dari sekadar dorongan,\Ndasar bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hasil kerjamu menyelamatkanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Presdir menjelaskan semuanya kepada staf.\NAku tak perlu berhenti kerja!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang kecurigaan itu hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak untuk semuanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian bisa tentukan pelaku sebenarnya\Ndalam waktu singkat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat kalian, kecurigaan pada klienku\Nbisa teratasi sebelum memburuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal kalian juga sibuk\Ndengan banyak kasus lainnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka mengatur jadwal kami\Nagar semuanya beres.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami membagi tiga pekerjaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako menyarankan\Nuntuk melakukan hal itu sejak awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka melakukan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia ingin melakukan\Napa pun sebisanya untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Aku tidak berbuat banyak sama sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya berusaha memberi dukungan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga minta maaf, seharusnya\Naku hanya menjadi staf administrasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak... tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun buktinya kurang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa suara Akira\Nmengandung sedikit kemarahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tidak boleh mengatakan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat kau, kami bisa membantu klien kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai ucapan terima kasih,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bagaimana kalau kita jalan-jalan kantor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, bagus! Pegunungan!\NAku ingin pergi ke pegunungan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ide bagus. Bagaimana kalau berkemah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak kapan kau ikut?\NKau tidak bekerja di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kita pergi ke gunung\Nyang ada perkemahannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sabar untuk mendirikan tenda\Ndan membuat api unggun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Daichi, ayo kita menyetir ke sana!\N- Ini pasti seru, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak keberatan,\Ntapi apa kau tak ada pekerjaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira kembali normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ya, pasti!\N- Aku akan mengambil cuti!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pegunungan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perkemahan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, kalian harus membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei. Pengacara, kau sedang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alat pengasapanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, kenapa kau memakai kacamata hitam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlihat sangat keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di tempat banyak pohon,\Nmungkin mata tertusuk dahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini langkah pencegahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang bisa kubantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kau giling biji kopi ini\Nagar mudah digunakan nanti?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, aku tidak tahu cara mendirikan tenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kau bisa potong kayu bakar?\NItu mudah, tak perlu kapak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Madaraito, kau pasti benar-benar\Nsuka berkemah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menyiapkan hampir semua peralatan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin sekarang tidak terlihat begitu,\Ntapi dulu aku benci pegunungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku jadi menyukainya berkat Daichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau jalan-jalan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suaranya sangat menyegarkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juga angin dan aromanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita perlu berjalan lebih lambat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, ini pas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penghalangnya berakhir di sini,\Njadi kita berjalan di sisi dalam jalan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang ada di balik penghalang itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lereng curam seperti tebing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah. Jika sampai jatuh, itu bencana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sekarang\Naku bisa tenang bersamamu, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga bisa tenang\Njika kau berada di sisiku, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira pernah memiliki\Npengalaman menakutkan di pegunungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah jalan-jalan ke pegunungan\Nadalah ide buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm... Memang benar\Naku punya trauma masa lalu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku merasa\Nbisa pergi ke mana pun bersamamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar lupa akan traumaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta-Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah. Ada bangku di depan.\NMau istirahat sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak sehebat yang kau kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau membantu\Nkasus wanita tak terlihat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu niatku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau marah, dan itu tidak sering terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf. Apakah aku membuatmu takut?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, tidak, aku tidak bermaksud begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membayangkan bagaimana rasanya\Njika orang-orang mencurigaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemudian, aku jadi sangat sedih\Ndan merasa frustrasi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, tapi jika dipikir-pikir, aku melewati\Nbatas cakupan pekerjaanku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan memikirkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sensasi, panas tubuh, dan aroma Akira\Ntiba-tiba begitu dekat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tak terlihat\Nselalu dipandang dengan curiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat kau dan lainnya,\Nkita bisa bersihkan nama klien sepenuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi saat ini, lebih dari itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Akira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira terasa panas sekali di punggungku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak suka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku suka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baru saja mentertawakanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa rasakan tubuhmu sedikit bergetar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mengetahui tiap emosiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu membuatku lebih bahagia\Ndibanding apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kau lebih mengenalku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Anu, apakah itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menciummu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktunya tidak tepat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, bukan begitu, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita kembali?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kita... tetap di sini\Nsedikit lebih lama lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau melakukannya sekali lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu, anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan menentangnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo? Kenapa mereka berdua lama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini. Kupas semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa berkemah tanpa kari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini membawa kembali kenangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi aku sudah bilang\Ndulu aku benci pegunungan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat membencinya sampai merasa getir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan ingin menuntut siapa pun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang berpikir untuk mendaki gunung\Nuntuk karyawisata.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Madaraito, kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian bisa jalan terus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yakin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, pergi saja. Aku akan pelan-pelan saja\Ndan menyusul kalian nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan tertinggal jauh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karyawisata bodoh ini harusnya mati!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:13:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kikira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sekelas, tapi aku belum pernah\Nberbicara dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus. Itu melegakan.\NMasih ada orang di belakang sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untung aku bisa melihat Kikira.\NJika tidak, aku takkan terus mendaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku... sudah tidak kuat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kikira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Te-Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebentar! Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau membuatku merasa bersalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Njangan tertinggal, bisa? Agh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?! Sekarang dia sangat kasar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian lama juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:15:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya sudah selesai makan siang.\NMereka sedang bermain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kikira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih untuk yang tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keberatan jika kita makan bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke-Kenapa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku, kita bukan teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi... Kita bukan teman,\Ntapi kau tetap membantuku tadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu seperti memberikan tempat duduk\Nkepada orang tua di kereta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku seperti orang tua?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Argh! Makan siang sendirian\Nsangat canggung bagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanlah bersamaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hmph. Ya, terserahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.\NKikira hanya canggung secara sosial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pantas orang tidak mau bergaul dengannya\Npadahal dia berwajah tampan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, anggaplah sebagai ucapan terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayam gorengmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak menahan diri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, boleh aku duduk di sebelahmu di bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, terserah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tertidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kikira juga tertidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat aku tidur...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini akan terasa canggung ketika dia bangun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus memastikan\Naku tidak membangunkannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya sedikit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan tidur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa?! Tapi tadi kau baru tidur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu, kita bisa\Nterus duduk seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah awalnya,\Ndan kami mulai bersama setelah itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, dia selalu sulit dihadapi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian duduk bersama\Nsepanjang waktu?! Indahnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungai di sini tidak terlalu deras.\NKelihatannya cukup bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kita juga\Nbisa memancing di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bisa tahu kau tajam\Nhanya dari tubuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bisa tahu kau besar\Nhanya dari perutmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menggelar kain di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana Shizuka dan Tonome?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka bilang akan menyusul sebentar lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ja-Jarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah ada masalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jarashi pergi lebih dulu.\NMau kupanggilkan dia kembali untukmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa tidak apa-apa kau saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kau masuk ke tenda?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah pakai baju renang ini.\NKurasa ada sesuatu yang salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, bukan apa-apa. Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, rumbainya tersangkut di talinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, sudah kuduga ada yang tidak beres.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kau yang memilih\Nbaju renang ini, Shizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, bukan.\NJarashi memilihkannya untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sangat manis dan cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?! Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Dia terlalu manis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baju renangnya termasuk ini juga.\NHaruskah aku memakainya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, pakailah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, kau manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh! Ada banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Rasanya luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, ikannya pergi ke arahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu luar biasa, Jarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kaget...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kau\Nmencobanya juga, Tonome?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan tidak bisa mendekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, aku tidak pernah menyadarinya,\Ntapi apakah tubuhmu bagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bajumu menempel di tubuh karena basah,\Njadi aku bisa melihat bentuk tubuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira memiliki tubuh yang bagus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Akira, mungkin kau harus melepas bajumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti sulit bergerak dengan baju basah itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku... lebih suka tidak melakukan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu, bagaimana bilangnya, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagiku, jika aku melepas baju, kalian bisa\Nmengintip ke celana dalamku dari atas,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan, itu akan agak memalukan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak begitu mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tidak begitu mengerti.\NBagaimanapun, kami tidak bisa melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun juga, itu terasa memalukan\Nbagi kami, manusia tak terlihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Jarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangkap ikan lagi.\NKita akan memakannya untuk makan siang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ide bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira, anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku mengajukan permintaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm? Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan biarkan\Norang lain menemukanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau sesuatu seperti itu, mungkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku minta maaf mengenai itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ingin menyela, tapi bisakah\Nkalian mencari ruang tertutup?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa tidur jika mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau ingin bergantian\Ndan aku yang menyetir, beri tahu aku, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan mengandalkan\Norang yang menguap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu menyakitkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau selalu baik, tapi dengan cara\Nyang paling kejam. Aku suka itu darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan ini?\NUcapanmu tidak masuk akal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka semua tertidur lelap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang merasa sangat mengantuk\Nsetelah melakukan perjalanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi... aku masih terjaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.95,0:22:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali, mungkin hanya kita berdua...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, mungkin ini terlalu cepat.
